{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_01_05",
  "title": "サニーピース 01 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "オーディション、不合格かぁ……\nやっぱり私には無理だったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I failed the audition…\nI guess it really was impossible for me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.1087528229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私なんかがアイドルになれる訳ない……\nそんなの、やる前から分かってたことなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way someone like me could be an idol…\nI knew that before I even tried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4333333333,
      "endTime": 18.3603856722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "……どうして？\nどうして涙が止まらないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why?\nWhy can't I stop crying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5333333333,
      "endTime": 22.4945807935,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.333333400001,
          "startTime": 22.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……どうして泣いてるの？\n不合格がそんなにショックだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… why are you crying?\nAre you that upset about failing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "endTime": 30.0824706401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "分かんない……\n分かんないけど、悔しいの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know…\nBut I feel frustrated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2666666667,
      "endTime": 35.578072881900006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんみたいになれないって分かってるのに……\n私なんて……オーディションに落ちて当然なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I can't be like Saki-chan…\nSomeone like me… it's only natural that I failed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7666666667,
      "endTime": 43.9030616127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "悔しいの……悔しくて、涙が止まらないの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm frustrated… I'm so frustrated that I can't stop crying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1,
      "endTime": 49.406145000500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "泣くほど悔しいなんて\n千紗は本気でアイドルになりたかったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're crying because you're so frustrated…\nyou must have really wanted to become an idol‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9,
      "endTime": 55.131330579600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "本気で、アイドルに……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously… an idol…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333333333,
      "endTime": 58.4290021737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、私はアイドルになりたかったんだ……\nこんなに強く、アイドルになりたいって思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I did want to be an idol…\nI wanted to be an idol this badly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8,
      "endTime": 71.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……私、悔しいよ……\n諦めたくないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan… I'm frustrated…\nI don't want to give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0333333333,
      "endTime": 80.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "私……アイドルになりたいよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I want to be an idol…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6666666667,
      "endTime": 84.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4532908122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ならなれるわ\n私も応援するから、二人でアイドルになりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can do it‚ Chisa.\nI'll support you‚ so let's become idols together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1279734295,
      "endTime": 92.4120032812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.6279734295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "うん……待ってて、お姉ちゃん……\n必ず追いつくから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I'll catch up to you‚ Saki-chan…\nI'll definitely catch up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6279734295,
      "endTime": 97.64409223620001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0279734295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所にはなれなかったけど\nいつか必ず、同じステージに立ってみせるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we couldn't be in the same agency‚\nI'll definitely stand on the same stage as you someday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0279734295,
      "endTime": 105.5587359366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5279734295,
      "endTime": 107.7279734295,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2100.0000000000086,
          "startTime": 108.6279734295
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6833.333333300005,
          "startTime": 113.3613067628
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1294325126
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.1294325126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "……え、電話？\n知らない番号から……誰だろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? A phone call?\nIt's from an unknown number… I wonder who it is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1613067628,
      "endTime": 115.0946404141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、白石千紗さんですか？\n私は星見プロの――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ is this Chisa Shiraishi-san?\nI'm from Hoshimi Pro――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4613067628,
      "endTime": 120.2822534367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.4946400961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、星見プロ？\nどうして……私、オーディションに落ちたんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ Hoshimi Pro?\nWhy…? I failed the audition‚ didn't I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4946400961,
      "endTime": 128.3973798252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.5946400961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……すみません\n残念ですがオーディションは不合格です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ about that… I'm sorry‚\nbut unfortunately‚ you didn't pass the audition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5946400961,
      "endTime": 134.0317313382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、私個人としてはあなたに光るものを感じました\nだから一つだけ確認させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I personally saw something special in you.\nSo I'd like to confirm one thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4613067628,
      "endTime": 141.2279734295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんと同じ事務所になれなくても\nあなたはアイドルになりたいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you can't be in the same agency as your sister‚\ndo you still want to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4613067628,
      "endTime": 146.3873674024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.5946400961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、アイドルになりたいです\nこれからもアイドルを目指すつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I want to be an idol.\nI'm still going to pursue that dream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5946400961,
      "endTime": 153.0075122175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.1946400961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
