      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_05-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションに落ちた時から、お姉ちゃんと\n同じグループにはなれないって覚悟してたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had prepared myself for the possibility of not being\nin the same group as Saki-chan ever since I failed the audition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.0279734295,
      "endTime": 233.07509336479998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
