      "text": "いざデビューが近づくと不安になって……\n私一人でアイドルに……そんなの無理だよ、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as our debut approached‚ I started to feel anxious…\nMe‚ being an idol alone… There's no way I could do that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.5279734295,
      "endTime": 242.4255979672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
